OL,3,CHundreds gather to honour 19-year-old
OL,4,Cpolice officer who died on duty
OL,6,FA 19-year-old officer who died after
OL,7,Fshe was hit by a car while on duty was
OL,8,Fgiven full police honours as hundreds
OL,9,Fgathered for her funeral.
OL,11,FPc Jess Turnbull, who had only joined
OL,12,FNorthumbria Police in September, was
OL,13,Fcalled to a collision on the A189 near
OL,14,FCramlington, Northumberland, at around
OL,15,F11.10pm on 8 June.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
