OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1784285298
OL,3,CHundreds gather to honour 19-year-old
OL,4,Cpolice officer who died on duty
OL,6,FNorthumbria Police said that while she
OL,7,Fwas out of her marked police vehicle
OL,8,Fat the scene, Pc Turnbull was struck
OL,9,Fby a car. The vehicle that struck her
OL,10,Fwas unconnected to the original
OL,11,Fincident.
OL,13,FPc Turnbull died in hospital on
OL,14,FWednesday 10 June surrounded by her
OL,15,Floved ones.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
