FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1784285298
OL,3,CHundreds gather to honour 19-year-old
OL,4,Cpolice officer who died on duty
OL,6,FOn Friday 10 July, Pc Turnbull's
OL,7,Fcoffin was escorted to Newcastle
OL,8,FCathedral by horses, pipers and
OL,9,Fmotorcycle outriders as it passed a
OL,10,Fguard of honour, with flags from
OL,11,Fforces across the UK.
OL,13,FThe parade was led by seven pipers and
OL,14,Fa lone drummer followed by the four
OL,15,Fmounted officers.
OL,17,FPc Turnbull's coffin, which was draped
OL,18,Fin a union flag, was carried into the
OL,19,Fchurch by more uniformed officers as
OL,20,Fthe pipers played 'Amazing Grace'.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
