OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1784285298
OL,3,CHundreds gather to honour 19-year-old
OL,4,Cpolice officer who died on duty
OL,6,FThe officer's police hat was placed on
OL,7,Ftop of the coffin as it was carried
OL,8,Fthrough the main door, past
OL,9,Fdignitaries including Northumbria
OL,10,FChief Constable Vanessa Jardine, who
OL,11,Fsaluted.
OL,13,FPc Turnbull's parents followed the
OL,14,Fcoffin into the church, followed by
OL,15,Fmany more family members and dozens of
OL,16,Fofficers.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
