PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1784285298
OL,3,CHundreds gather to honour 19-year-old
OL,4,Cpolice officer who died on duty
OL,6,FNorthumbria Police previously said
OL,7,Fthat a 73-year-old Mercedes driver was
OL,8,Farrested on suspicion of causing death
OL,9,Fby dangerous driving, and has been
OL,10,Fbailed.
OL,12,FOfficers continue to investigate what
OL,13,Fhappened and asked anyone with
OL,14,Finformation to come forward.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/5
